1
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,950
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,350 --> 00:01:37,830
[Episode 8]

3
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:01,790
Xiaolan.

4
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:05,560
I'm Susu.

5
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,310
I'm Susu, Xiaolan.

6
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:11,590
Susu?

7
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:13,630
It's me.

8
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:14,470
Xiaolan.

9
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:18,510
[Fang Mulan, the only daughter
of the Fang family in Nanyang]

10
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:16,910
Susu?

11
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,400
I know you.

12
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:29,840
No.

13
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:31,120
I don't know you.

14
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:32,590
I don't know you.

15
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,610
I don't know you!

16
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,890
I don't know you!

17
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,890
I don't know you!

18
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,520
I don't know you!

19
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:44,870
Who did this?

20
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:46,750
Was it Huo Mingxi?

21
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,240
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

22
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,960
I'm sorry! I'll never run away again!

23
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,710
I'm sorry! I'll never run away again!

24
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:56,710
I'll never run away again!

25
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:58,590
I'll take off my clothes
and sing for you, okay?

26
00:02:58,590 --> 00:02:59,710
I'll sing for you.

27
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:01,240
I'm a good girl.

28
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,080
I'm not human!

29
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,150
I'm not human!

30
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:04,590
I'm just a doll!

31
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:05,590
I'll sing for you.

32
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:10,360
Xiaolan!

33
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,360
I'm sorry.

34
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,680
I came too late.

35
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,480
I'll take you out of here.

36
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,030
I'll take you out of here.

37
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:22,480
I'll take you out of here.

38
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:24,120
Xiaolan,

39
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,520
I'm here.

40
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:33,390
[Huo Mingxi,
Master of the Huo Family's Branch]

41
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:43,190
Who are you?

42
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,960
Little girl.

43
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,590
You came right to my door.

44
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,960
You beast!

45
00:03:57,590 --> 00:03:58,870
How dare you hit me!

46
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,400
I'll kill you!

47
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:32,640
Let's go!

48
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:36,550
They're not here!

49
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,560
Not here either!

50
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,090
Let's go!

51
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:48,870
Xiaolan.

52
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:49,950
Xiaolan?

53
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,680
Xiaolan!

54
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,040
The doctor said

55
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,950
she was covered in wounds,

56
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:02,080
had recently suffered a miscarriage,

57
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,560
and had been bleeding continuously

58
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,360
without receiving any medical treatment.

59
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:08,360
I don't know how she survived until now.

60
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,160
Think of something else.

61
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,720
There must be a way.

62
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:22,920
Susu.

63
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:27,510
Xiaolan.

64
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:29,510
You recognized us?

65
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,680
Qing, you have grown so tall.

66
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:39,310
Susu, you're so pretty.

67
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,720
You are both big girls now.

68
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,930
You only praise me for being tall,

69
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:46,830
not for being pretty.

70
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,890
You're playing favorites.

71
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:53,870
How did you leave the orphanage?

72
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,480
Did Nanny sell you?

73
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,040
Were you taken by the Huo family?

74
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,950
Don't worry.

75
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:03,040
We all escaped from the orphanage.

76
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,600
No one will hurt us anymore.

77
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:07,630
Good.

78
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,070
That's good.

79
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,480
It's so good...

80
00:06:13,070 --> 00:06:13,870
to see you.

81
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:15,870
Yes.

82
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,190
We will never be apart again.

83
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:24,120
Susu.

84
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,480
We killed Huo Mingxi.

85
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:31,090
The Huo family
will definitely take revenge.

86
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:32,760
I'm not going to make it.

87
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:36,210
You need to leave Beicheng immediately.

88
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,450
We will never leave you behind.

89
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,120
I don't want to part with you either.

90
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,830
After I die,

91
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:52,430
take my ashes

92
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,310
back to Nanyang,

93
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,510
alright?

94
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:01,270
Alright.

95
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:06,810
I'll take you home.

96
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,270
I remember you said

97
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,160
Nanyang was your home.

98
00:07:14,950 --> 00:07:16,680
When I was 9,

99
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,800
I was trafficked.

100
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,360
It's been 13 years.

101
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,510
I almost forgot my father's face.

102
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,920
I really...

103
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,360
really want to go home.

104
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:39,360
It hurts.

105
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,600
Sing me another song.

106
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:43,800
Okay.

107
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,800
Sing that one.

108
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,390
I will.

109
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,190
I'll sing it, Xiaolan.

110
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,240
Get some good sleep.

111
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,900
It won't hurt when you wake up.

112
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:55,780
♪ Spring comes and autumn goes ♪

113
00:07:56,650 --> 00:07:58,740
♪ Time flows like a river ♪

114
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:02,920
♪ The wanderer grows weary
of drifting afar ♪

115
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:06,810
♪ Memories of childhood days ♪

116
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,780
♪ Spent playing at home ♪

117
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:13,840
♪ Feel as vivid as yesterday ♪

118
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:18,300
♪ Three thatched cottages ♪

119
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:20,980
♪ An old plum tree ♪

120
00:08:21,770 --> 00:08:25,440
♪ We played hide-and-seek beneath it ♪

121
00:08:27,130 --> 00:08:29,310
♪ Birds sang on the branches ♪

122
00:08:30,170 --> 00:08:32,240
♪ Fish swam in the stream ♪

123
00:08:33,130 --> 00:08:36,490
♪ Those were the simple joys
of carefree days ♪

124
00:08:38,010 --> 00:08:40,679
♪ The happiness of childhood ♪

125
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,270
Dad...

126
00:08:47,110 --> 00:08:48,110
Dad...

127
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:57,910
Xiaolan.

128
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,870
Xiaolan.

129
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:02,960
-Xiaolan.
-Xiaolan.

130
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,030
Xiaolan...

131
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:08,510
Xiaolan...

132
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:10,870
We will take you home.

133
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,240
[Beicheng]

134
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:40,670
Stay highly alert, everyone!

135
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,550
Search carefully!

136
00:09:42,870 --> 00:09:45,480
Even if you have to
turn the station upside down,

137
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,960
you must find them!

138
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,720
The Huos haven't seen you before.

139
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,910
Take Xiaolan and go first.

140
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:03,770
What about you?

141
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:06,120
I'll lead them away.

142
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,650
I'll meet up with you later.

143
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,320
Go!

144
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,460
Take the gun to protect yourself.

145
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,750
Be careful.

146
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:52,360
Found her! Over there!

147
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,000
Where?

148
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,030
Move!

149
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:58,960
Watch out!

150
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,020
What are you doing?

151
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:02,840
Stop!

152
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,150
Don't run!

153
00:11:11,550 --> 00:11:12,080
Over there!

154
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,200
-Hurry! Over there!
-Stop!

155
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:13,960
-Over there!
-Stop!

156
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:14,440
-Come here now!
-Hurry!

157
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:14,870
Stop!

158
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:15,480
Stop!

159
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:16,880
[Beicheng to Feng'an]

160
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:16,870
-Stop!
-Stop!

161
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,870
-Stop!
-Stop!

162
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:18,960
Stop!

163
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,030
Stop!

164
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,320
-Stop her!
-Stop!

165
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,000
Don't run!

166
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,870
She's on the train!

167
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:23,790
Hurry, get on!

168
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:27,610
[Beicheng]

169
00:12:13,870 --> 00:12:14,670
Susu!

170
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:21,870
Susu!

171
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:24,200
Leave here.

172
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:27,970
On the day you left,

173
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:30,120
the gentian flowers were blooming.

174
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,120
Didn't you say

175
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:33,180
you would show me the view?

176
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:46,540
I was planning
to sacrifice myself that day,

177
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:48,720
so my companion
could carry Xiaolan's ashes

178
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,790
safely back south.

179
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:52,050
But I didn't expect you

180
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,750
to follow me onto the train.

181
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:58,440
So I said those words to you,

182
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:01,150
trying to provoke you into leaving.

183
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,320
Get lost!

184
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:10,930
Don't you understand?

185
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,080
I approached you

186
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:14,150
only to use you.

187
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,120
Do you think

188
00:13:16,790 --> 00:13:18,240
I really would like you?

189
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:27,910
If what you say is true...

190
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,340
then pull the trigger.

191
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:38,510
Susu!

192
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:39,850
What are you doing?

193
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,320
Just pretend that

194
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:45,720
you've never known me.

195
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,510
I had a death wish back then.

196
00:13:58,390 --> 00:13:59,440
Letting the Huo family see you

197
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:01,120
deal with the murderer yourself

198
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,780
could clear you of suspicion,

199
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:05,520
which would clear the debt between us.

200
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,510
But I didn't expect

201
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,260
the Huo family to treat you like that.

202
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,270
So,

203
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:40,570
you only approached me from the beginning

204
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,600
to save someone?

205
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:45,150
On the train 3 years ago,

206
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,960
why didn't you explain?

207
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,910
Since you survived,

208
00:14:53,630 --> 00:14:54,960
why didn't you come back

209
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,090
to find me over the past 3 years?

210
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:59,840
And since you knew
about my family situation,

211
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,440
why did you have to pretend
to be Fang Mulan

212
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,840
and marry my brother?

213
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,880
What exactly do you want?

214
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,320
You have too many questions.

215
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,670
That's another story,

216
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:11,730
and it comes at a different price.

217
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,270
Fine.

218
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,200
What price?

219
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:23,030
If I asked you to kill someone for me,

220
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,240
would you do it?

221
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,240
Kill who?

222
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,080
Master Huo.

223
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,670
Master Huo?

224
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:56,390
What are you doing?

225
00:15:56,390 --> 00:15:57,720
Are you going to
crash straight into Master Huo

226
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:59,270
and take everyone down with him?

227
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:01,130
Isn't this exactly what you want?

228
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:05,440
What do you mean?

229
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:07,220
Someone tampered with

230
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:09,910
this plane, right?

231
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,440
You could fool others,

232
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,530
but I've known it all along.

233
00:16:17,270 --> 00:16:19,800
You must have had an ulterior motive
in making

234
00:16:20,510 --> 00:16:22,510
the aviation school's opening ceremony
happen.

235
00:16:22,510 --> 00:16:23,510
At the banquet,

236
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,480
you seemed uneasy.

237
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:28,030
I also saw a foreign woman

238
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:29,480
snooping around the plane

239
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:30,550
several times.

240
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,120
Tell me,

241
00:16:48,550 --> 00:16:49,810
what exactly did she do

242
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,270
to this plane?

243
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,330
Explosives.

244
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:58,870
Explosives?

245
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,000
Explosives.

246
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:07,589
No wonder.

247
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:09,310
You didn't want my brother
to get on the plane,

248
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:10,480
but you were willing to let me.

249
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,810
Didn't I try to stop you?

250
00:17:13,829 --> 00:17:14,589
Ren Susu,

251
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:16,339
where are the explosives?

252
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,130
I don't know.

253
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:19,560
There's still time to land.

254
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:20,640
What do you mean you don't know?

255
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:22,270
What do you mean there's still time?

256
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:23,829
There's still time for you
to kill Master Huo with the explosives

257
00:17:23,829 --> 00:17:25,030
in front of everyone?

258
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:26,349
Have you thought about a way out?

259
00:17:26,349 --> 00:17:27,200
Are you crazy?

260
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:28,750
I told you,

261
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:31,760
what I do has nothing to do with you.

262
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:35,480
Then why are you on the same plane as me?

263
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:36,720
Do you want to die with me,

264
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:38,400
or do you just not want to waste a bomb?

265
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,930
Whatever you're planning,

266
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,080
you don't have what it takes.

267
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,520
Why are you being so foolish?

268
00:17:44,790 --> 00:17:45,650
After landing,

269
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:46,640
listen to me.

270
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:48,480
Stop messing with the Huo family.

271
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:49,400
Stay by my side,

272
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,490
and I will keep you safe.

273
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,270
You?

274
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:55,070
You are too naive.

275
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:56,030
Me? Naive?

276
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:57,880
Fine.

277
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:01,880
What are you doing?

278
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,960
Rather than watching you throw your life away
because of your foolishness,

279
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:05,310
I might as well send you off myself.

280
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:07,030
That way, you won't end up
like you did 3 years ago,

281
00:18:07,030 --> 00:18:09,490
failing to save others
and hurting yourself

282
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:12,140
while dragging innocent people into it.

283
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:15,400
I don't need you to send me off.

284
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,110
And I will never drag you into this.

285
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,440
There's a parachute behind me.

286
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,970
Put it on and get out of here!

287
00:18:22,510 --> 00:18:23,840
Are you out of your mind?

288
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:31,720
Something fell off!

289
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,640
Principal,

290
00:18:39,030 --> 00:18:40,160
something is wrong.

291
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,820
Do I even care about life or death?

292
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,000
Ren Susu.

293
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:58,720
Those who survive suffer even more!

294
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:01,640
Is that so?

295
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:03,530
Did the dead tell you that?

296
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:05,050
Let's play a game then.

297
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:07,480
There is only one parachute left now.

298
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:08,480
The winner gets to live.

299
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,210
The loser...

300
00:19:09,550 --> 00:19:10,440
dies.

301
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,560
♪ How much love ♪

302
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:16,810
♪ Is enough to be wasted? ♪

303
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:16,590
Fine.

304
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:17,920
What game?

305
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:21,020
♪ I haven't forgiven you ♪

306
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:23,240
♪ So don't you forgive me ♪

307
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:25,660
Why is this plane giving off black smoke?

308
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:27,300
♪ Let the wildfire ♪

309
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:30,810
♪ Consume us and burn us to ashes ♪

310
00:19:32,110 --> 00:19:32,750
Come on!

311
00:19:32,380 --> 00:19:34,460
♪ Still, we choose to be moths ♪

312
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:36,760
♪ Flying into the flames ♪

313
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:37,590
Do you love me

314
00:19:38,070 --> 00:19:39,030
or hate me?

315
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:40,950
♪ Must it take heartache ♪

316
00:19:41,090 --> 00:19:42,870
♪ To know my heart belongs to you? ♪

317
00:19:44,010 --> 00:19:45,630
♪ Hearts cold no more ♪

318
00:19:45,770 --> 00:19:47,240
♪ Is every sweet dream ♪

319
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:49,050
♪ Destined to fade away? ♪

320
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:48,440
I hate you!

321
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:50,680
I hate you so much
I want to tear you apart!

322
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,230
♪ Don't let it end in smoke ♪

323
00:19:52,330 --> 00:19:55,500
♪ Love and hate till the very end ♪

324
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:53,680
Correct.

325
00:19:55,650 --> 00:19:58,050
♪ Hold nothing back ♪

326
00:19:59,000 --> 00:19:59,920
Then let me ask you.

327
00:19:59,410 --> 00:20:02,140
♪ Never back down, hold my ground ♪

328
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,310
Do you love me

329
00:20:02,290 --> 00:20:04,770
♪ Till I've given my all ♪

330
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:03,270
or hate me?

331
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:05,900
♪ We ♪

332
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:08,960
♪ Must be together ♪

333
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,130
Take a guess.

334
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:12,340
♪ Forevermore ♪

335
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,350
You hate me.

336
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:22,750
Good.

337
00:20:23,070 --> 00:20:23,750
You won.

338
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,400
Susu!

339
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:33,820
♪ Take away everything I have ♪

340
00:20:33,860 --> 00:20:35,770
♪ Can you bear the weight of it all? ♪

341
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,260
It looks like someone was thrown out.

342
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:38,790
♪ I offer you my whole life ♪

343
00:20:37,510 --> 00:20:38,570
Call an ambulance!

344
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,510
Evacuate the crowd immediately!

345
00:20:38,910 --> 00:20:40,320
♪ In exchange for my everything ♪

346
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:39,920
Hurry up

347
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:40,790
Bravo!

348
00:20:40,420 --> 00:20:42,290
♪ Will you finally be mine? ♪

349
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:45,430
♪ Give me love and hate ♪

350
00:20:45,570 --> 00:20:48,760
♪ Let the tears fall,
let the blood spill ♪

351
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:51,080
♪ Even through suffering,
I'll never let go of your hand ♪

352
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:52,380
♪ We ♪

353
00:20:53,830 --> 00:20:55,430
♪ Remain bound by fate until the end ♪

354
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,110
Ren Susu.

355
00:20:56,760 --> 00:21:00,880
♪ Forevermore ♪

356
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:57,880
You got guts.

357
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,200
See?

358
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:06,910
You can never be ruthless
at a critical moment.

359
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:08,160
So in the future,

360
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:10,610
don't pretend to be ruthless anymore.

361
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:12,680
Murong Qingyi,

362
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:15,000
we should have

363
00:21:15,590 --> 00:21:16,990
said goodbye 3 years ago.

364
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,400
I let you down.

365
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:22,240
But now you have a new life.

366
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,440
Stay away from me

367
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:26,590
and live on.

368
00:21:38,350 --> 00:21:39,000
Susu!

369
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:57,670
I've told you everything

370
00:21:58,030 --> 00:21:59,270
you wanted to know

371
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:01,850
and everything you had doubts about.

372
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:04,000
And where I'm going,

373
00:22:04,510 --> 00:22:06,570
I'll get there even if I have to crawl.

374
00:22:07,070 --> 00:22:08,830
But that is not where you're going.

375
00:22:08,830 --> 00:22:09,480
Also,

376
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,260
now that we've landed,

377
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:15,330
you should call me sister-in-law.

378
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:21,240
Ren Susu.

379
00:22:23,030 --> 00:22:24,400
You are a liar.

380
00:22:37,110 --> 00:22:37,790
Over here.

381
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:41,920
Qingyi!

382
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:43,720
Qingyi!

383
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,720
How are you doing?

384
00:22:50,550 --> 00:22:51,400
I won't die.

385
00:22:59,790 --> 00:23:01,520
Cordon off the plane wreckage.

386
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:03,010
Get someone to inspect it.

387
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:05,400
If any problems are found, keep it quiet

388
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:06,330
and report to me.

389
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:07,030
Yes.

390
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,600
Why are you looking at me?

391
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:29,550
Everyone ran out to save you two,

392
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:30,590
and I hurt my foot

393
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:32,790
while people were pushing and shoving.

394
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,880
What happened?

395
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:39,750
Why did you risk your life
to follow Murong Qingyi

396
00:23:39,750 --> 00:23:41,150
and jump out of the plane?

397
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:43,090
Are you really not afraid of death?

398
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:45,680
What else could I do?

399
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,960
I had to clean up

400
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:49,640
Tasia's mess.

401
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:53,510
It was indeed a close call this time.

402
00:23:53,550 --> 00:23:55,950
But luckily, no innocent people were hurt,

403
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:58,700
and the Huo family
didn't suspect anything.

404
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:01,890
What on earth did you talk about
with Murong Qingyi?

405
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:04,480
He interrogated me,

406
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:07,000
asking where I've been
for the past 3 years,

407
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,060
and why I came back.

408
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,000
He also asked me...

409
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,790
Do you love me or hate me?

410
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:20,410
He asked if you had ever loved him?

411
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,640
How do you know?

412
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,550
Isn't it always the same old thing

413
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:26,400
between a man and a woman
in those stories?

414
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:27,330
What did you say?

415
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:31,060
I just said something to get out of it.

416
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:33,110
He really can't wrap his head around it.

417
00:24:33,110 --> 00:24:34,920
Where else could you have been
these 3 years?

418
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:36,960
Does he really think
playing someone else is so easy?

419
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:39,360
Of course you've been training in Nanyang.

420
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:45,480
Susu,

421
00:24:45,790 --> 00:24:46,720
do you have feelings for him?

422
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,590
I wouldn't.

423
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:47,010
[Murong Residence]

424
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:58,970
I don't want to drink it.

425
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:00,160
It's disgusting.

426
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:03,000
I had Mrs. Wang add rock sugar to it.

427
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,130
It's not bitter.

428
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:05,410
Have a taste.

429
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:10,400
You didn't go to Miss Fang
to show her your concern,

430
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:12,130
but instead brought soup to me?

431
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,920
You don't have
your sister-in-law's skills.

432
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:16,350
She used you as a shield

433
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:18,110
and only suffered minor injuries.

434
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:19,770
She is now out watching a play.

435
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,160
If you ask me,

436
00:26:27,550 --> 00:26:30,280
Mother and I are the ones
who need to be nourished.

437
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:32,070
The opening ceremony

438
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:33,920
was ruined by him.

439
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:36,790
My Lady.

440
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:43,030
Tell me,

441
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,000
did you do it on purpose?

442
00:26:45,590 --> 00:26:47,750
You knew today was Qingyu's big day,

443
00:26:48,030 --> 00:26:49,920
and you deliberately caused trouble.

444
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:52,050
No wonder everyone says you're a jinx!

445
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,410
Go call all the servants in.

446
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:00,240
Yes.

447
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,020
Everyone, come in.

448
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:23,110
From today on,

449
00:27:24,510 --> 00:27:26,350
I don't want
to hear any disrespectful terms

450
00:27:26,350 --> 00:27:28,160
of address in this house again.

451
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:31,610
Some of you servants

452
00:27:32,110 --> 00:27:35,110
have been working in the Murong family
for a long time,

453
00:27:35,110 --> 00:27:36,750
so I overlooked your past use
of disrespectful terms

454
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:37,790
of address.

455
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:40,680
But starting today,

456
00:27:41,350 --> 00:27:42,750
if I hear it one more time,

457
00:27:44,310 --> 00:27:46,970
you will be expelled
from the Murong residence.

458
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,000
Understood?

459
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:51,290
Understood.

460
00:27:51,290 --> 00:27:52,200
Understood.

461
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:53,830
Get out.

462
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:01,680
Why were you so fierce?

463
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:03,400
You always

464
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:05,440
believe him and protect him.

465
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:06,770
He's my own brother.

466
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:08,370
If I don't believe him,

467
00:28:08,510 --> 00:28:09,710
who should I believe?

468
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:17,890
It's still a little bitter, isn't it?

469
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:19,930
Have a candy.

470
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,200
Jinrui is always like that.

471
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,160
Don't mind her.

472
00:28:47,510 --> 00:28:49,110
I don't care about her at all.

473
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:56,020
Sister-in-law fell from a plane,

474
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:58,640
yet she came out completely unharmed.

475
00:28:58,640 --> 00:29:00,270
This Miss Fang,
who was pampered growing up,

476
00:29:00,270 --> 00:29:01,480
is quite capable.

477
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:06,860
What are you trying to say now?

478
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,640
This Fang Mulan is no ordinary person.

479
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:15,480
Be careful.

480
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:20,170
You think too much.

481
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:21,960
Drink some more.

482
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:23,160
Get some rest early.

483
00:29:40,640 --> 00:29:43,350
The old dog Huo must die.

484
00:29:44,550 --> 00:29:45,790
You expected me to let

485
00:29:45,790 --> 00:29:47,830
such a good opportunity slip away?

486
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,270
I couldn't do that.

487
00:29:50,310 --> 00:29:52,110
If we also harm the innocent,

488
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,270
then what's the fundamental difference

489
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:55,880
between us and the Huo family?

490
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:57,280
If you hadn't stopped me,

491
00:29:57,750 --> 00:29:59,550
the old dog Huo
would have boarded the plane

492
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:00,590
and been blown up in the air.

493
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:02,310
Then there wouldn't be so much trouble.

494
00:30:02,310 --> 00:30:04,640
What about the aviation school teacher
who was flying the plane?

495
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:06,300
Should I have just let him die?

496
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:07,200
What?

497
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:10,940
Is your hatred
more important than his life?

498
00:30:13,270 --> 00:30:15,200
Just because you acted on your own,

499
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:16,680
Nanny Sun has now returned

500
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,590
to the orphanage unharmed.

501
00:30:20,270 --> 00:30:21,440
Our mission failed.

502
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:24,830
All the thrilling moments had played out,

503
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:26,630
and the plan was fully executed,

504
00:30:27,160 --> 00:30:27,960
but in the end,

505
00:30:28,350 --> 00:30:29,610
it all came to nothing.

506
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:32,470
It was like I was
performing a play on stage.

507
00:31:03,110 --> 00:31:04,510
Whenever I see him,

508
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:07,750
every old wound on my body

509
00:31:07,750 --> 00:31:09,590
festers

510
00:31:10,110 --> 00:31:11,240
and oozes pus again!

511
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:13,440
I wanted to hold back my hatred,

512
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:14,640
but I couldn't!

513
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:18,480
The stench of rotting flesh fills my nose!

514
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:21,200
Only when he dies...

515
00:31:22,110 --> 00:31:23,480
can I find peace.

516
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:30,440
If you had succeeded today,

517
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:32,110
such a quick death

518
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,640
would have been too easy

519
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:34,770
for that old dog Huo.

520
00:31:46,750 --> 00:31:47,750
Rest assured.

521
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:50,880
That old dog Huo—

522
00:31:52,510 --> 00:31:54,550
I will definitely make him pay

523
00:31:56,310 --> 00:31:57,840
and face the consequences.

524
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:05,000
The problem now

525
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:07,720
is what we should do about Nanny Sun.

526
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:10,590
With such a huge incident
at the aviation school today,

527
00:32:10,590 --> 00:32:14,350
the Huo family will definitely do
their best to protect the old dog Huo.

528
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:15,610
They will investigate

529
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:16,880
who blew up the plane,

530
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:19,350
so naturally
they won't have time to care about

531
00:32:19,350 --> 00:32:22,000
Nanny Sun,
who has just returned to the orphanage.

532
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:22,800
That's right.

533
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,680
The orphanage will be poorly guarded.

534
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:26,590
It's the perfect opportunity
to make a move.

535
00:32:26,590 --> 00:32:27,350
Let me do it.

536
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:28,320
I'll do it.

537
00:32:33,510 --> 00:32:35,170
I need to get some things back.

538
00:32:38,070 --> 00:32:38,790
Tasia,

539
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:41,160
I understand you have a valid reason,

540
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,750
but if you act on your own again

541
00:32:42,750 --> 00:32:44,080
without my permission,

542
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:47,290
don't blame me for showing no regard
for our sisterhood.

543
00:32:49,310 --> 00:32:50,070
Understood.

544
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:59,430
[Renxin Orphanage]

545
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,210
Stop dawdling!

546
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:16,010
What are you looking at?

547
00:33:31,110 --> 00:33:32,150
One-eye.

548
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:33,920
What are you doing here?

549
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:41,160
Get up, get up! Stand up!

550
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:43,590
I told you that

551
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:46,750
when those rich masters and madams
who can donate money are here,

552
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:48,880
you should hold this stupid doll

553
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:50,000
and cry your eyes out in front of them!

554
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,640
Cry hard!

555
00:33:51,960 --> 00:33:53,820
Cry until they give in and donate!

556
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:55,640
Look at you guys.

557
00:33:54,220 --> 00:33:56,250
♪ Fantasies reduced to ash ♪

558
00:33:56,030 --> 00:33:57,480
You can't bring in donations,

559
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:58,330
♪ In a raging fire ♪

560
00:33:57,790 --> 00:33:59,650
and you can't even work properly.

561
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,860
No one is allowed to eat tomorrow!

562
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,310
Come here and line up!

563
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:04,070
♪ Those caught in the wake ♪

564
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:06,040
♪ Now tell only gray lies ♪

565
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,110
Can't you hurry up?

566
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:10,880
You're such gluttons.

567
00:34:10,100 --> 00:34:11,250
♪ Willingly ♪

568
00:34:11,270 --> 00:34:13,179
♪ Surrendering the naive visage ♪

569
00:34:14,110 --> 00:34:14,840
Let's go!

570
00:34:14,699 --> 00:34:16,370
♪ Of the past ♪

571
00:34:20,690 --> 00:34:22,570
♪ With no expectation of dawn ♪

572
00:34:27,010 --> 00:34:29,070
♪ Wandering beneath a pitch-black sky ♪

573
00:34:29,250 --> 00:34:31,320
♪ I smell no sorrow ♪

574
